SUMMARY:Discount Movie Night  Project Hail Mary
DTSTAMP:20260321T224057Z
DTSTART:20260325T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:This looks like a fun and inspirational sci-fi move \\(along th
	e lines of "The Martian" I'm thinking\\). I've purchased a bunch of ticket
	s in the middle of the theater so we can sit together in the best D-BOX se
	ats for us again to really get into the movie! We'll also have regular sea
	ts for the 6:25pm showing. ~Claudette ️ TRAILER: https://youtu.be/P0XN3-n-2
	Lo?si=dUcm4R5RjCPlZ3tM ️ TICKETS: D-BOX - $17.00 Regular - $11.50 Reimburse
	 me for a ticket via: Eventbrite \\(fees apply\\): https://www.eventbrite.
	com/e/movie-night-project-hail-mary-tickets-1983694348195  Or get your own
	 - movie buffs\, sign up for membership for perks at https://refer.cinemar
	k.com/Claudette37.  Don't go by the RSVPs to see if there are still seats 
	with the group. Check comments for updates - I'll let you know when I don'
	t have any more left. No need to ask if I still have tickets.    Please ar
	rive no later than 10 mins before the showing time or contact me to let me
	 know your ETA\, otherwise we'll enter without you and you'll lose your ti
	cket. Refunds will ONLY be issued if this event is rescheduled\, cancelled
	 or if you send in a reimbursement and I no longer have tickets. WE WILL N
	OT BE OFFERING REFUNDS ON THIS EVENT. IF YOU CAN NO LONGER ATTEND AND CANC
	EL ANY TIME AFTER YOU RSVP\, YOU WILL NEED TO SELL YOUR SPOT TO SOMEONE EL
	SE. Let's meet in the sofa lounge behind the elevator. If people get there
	 before me\, ask others if they are with meetup. This is a joint venture w
	ith Eastside Social Club on meetup.  More people may be attending than wha
	t you see RSVP'd here.  https://www.meetup.com/eastsidesocialclub/events/3
	12570417\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/discount-movie-n
	ight-project-hail-mary/18291007/2026-03-24T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Event
	s
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/discount-movie-night-proj
	ect-hail-mary/18291007/2026-03-24T00
LOCATION:Cinemark Totem Lake and XD\, Wells Fargo\, 12516 Totem Lake Blvd N
	E\, Kirkland\, WA
