UID:ZFgXPLUI0VyfeLplLOTj8
SUMMARY:Living Large with Less Stuff
DTSTAMP:20260321T224057Z
DTSTART:20260326T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Downsize to the right size! Take the stress out of de-clutterin
	g with easy steps and practical advice for a successful transition. During
	 this event\, you will hear from the following speakers: Catherine Arendt\
	, downsizing expert and Aljoya’s At Your Service Manager\, works with fami
	lies from start to finish as they transition from their homes to retiremen
	t communities. Nicole Bates\, Relocation Consultant at Hansen Bros. Moving
	 & Storage and HB Move Management\, has assisted thousands of clients with
	 their moves and specializes in working with clients downsizing from a lon
	g-time home to a smaller living space. Complimentary valet parking will be
	 provided for your convenience.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/d
	etails/living-large-with-less-stuff/18305951/2026-03-26T00\n\nFrom SEAtoda
	y - Learning & Education
